text: Éric Casimir (born 20 February 1977) is a French gymnast. He competed in five events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Le Port, Réunion
